title: Дуплет
overview: Anya and Masha Gorbachev are sisters by their father, whom they have never seen. Fate brings them together in the same investigative department, where Anya serves as an investigator and Masha as an operative. They have different personalities and different approaches to work. But eternal contradictions and irreconcilable differences will be the key to the success of this couple, who will have to solve more than one crime together.
